Package: balancedSampling
Type: Package
Title: Cross-balanced samples according to one or more qualitative variable
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Sylvain",
           family = "Loiseau",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "sylvain.loiseau@univ-paris13.fr",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5249-9550"))
Maintainer: Sylvain Loiseau <sylvain.loiseau@univ-paris13.fr>
Description: Cross balanced sampling is a constrained randomization: a
partition of a population into several samples so that each modality of one or
several qualitative variables is equaly distributed across the samples.
